Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 07:19:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add stock-monitor: PSX + US market dashboard with investment
 signals

A self-contained Bun web app for watching Pakistani (PSX) and US stocks
in separate tabs. Live quotes come from the PSX data portal and Yahoo
Finance, fetched server-side with a 5-minute cache; any symbol whose
feed is unreachable falls back to deterministic per-day sample data,
with a header badge showing live/partial/sample mode.

The dashboard shows an equal-weight watchlist index, market breadth,
top gainer/decliner, a sortable watchlist table with 6-month sparklines,
and a detail chart with crosshair tooltip. A technical signal engine
(50-day trend, 1/3-month momentum, RSI-14, range position, volatility)
scores each stock 0-100 and surfaces ranked buy candidates with
plain-English rationale, plus a "treat with caution" list. Prominent
not-financial-advice disclaimer throughout.

Run with: bun stock-monitor/server.ts

